#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:4
msgid "Types of Awards"
msgstr "奖项类型"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:7
msgid "Advancing Awards"
msgstr "可晋级奖项"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:9
msgid ""
"There are 8 awards for FTC\\ |reg| teams (excluding optional awards). For "
"more information on the exact requirements for these awards, see |cm|."
msgstr "FTC\\ |reg| 团队可以获得8个奖项（不包括可选奖项）。有关这些奖项具体要求的详细信息，请参阅 |cm|。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst-1
msgid "Award hierarchy"
msgstr "奖项体系"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:15
msgid "These are:"
msgstr "它们是："

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:17
msgid ""
"**The Inspire Award** recognizes teams who excel in MCI, TA, and Think award"
" accomplishments. This team is an all-around inspiration for others."
msgstr "**启发奖** 旨在表彰在 MCI、TA 和 思维奖项方面取得优异成绩的团队。该团队全面激励他人。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Judges' Choice Award** recognizes a team whose unique efforts, "
"performance, or dynamics merit recognition, but does not fit into any of the"
" other award categories."
msgstr "**评委选择奖** 旨在表彰在工作、表现或活力方面具有独特价值，但不属于其他奖项类别的团队。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:25
msgid "Inspire Award"
msgstr "启发奖"

