#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:33
msgid ""
"The team that receives this award is a strong ambassador for FIRST programs "
"and a role model FIRST team. This team is a top contender for many other "
"judged awards and is a gracious competitor. The Inspire Award winner is an "
"inspiration to other teams, acting with Gracious Professionalism\\ |reg| "
"both on and off the playing FIELD. This team shares their experiences, "
"enthusiasm, and knowledge with other teams, sponsors, their community, and "
"the JUDGES. Working as a unit, this team will have shown success in "
"performing the task of designing and building a ROBOT."
msgstr ""
"获得此奖项的团队是 FIRST 项目的杰出代表，也是一个模范 FIRST "
"团队。该队是许多其他评审奖项的有力竞争者，也是一个高尚的竞争者。启发奖得主在赛场内外都以高尚的专业精神激励着其他团队。该团队与其他团队、赞助商、社区和评委分享他们的经验、热情和知识。通过团队合作，该团队表现出其成功完成了设计和制造机器人的任务。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:36
msgid ""
"A portfolio is required for this award. The Inspire Award is the top award "
"for an FTC team. It is given to a team that consistently rises to the top in"
" other awards categories."
msgstr "此奖项需提交作品集。启发奖是FTC团队的最高荣誉，授予在其他奖项类别中持续表现优异的团队。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:38
msgid ""
"Of all the awards, this one is arguably the most subjective, as it is about "
"how good a team does overall, including how much they weigh outreach as "
"compared to robot performance and documentation."
msgstr "在所有奖项中，这个奖项或许是最主观的，因为它关乎团队的整体表现——包括与机器人表现和文档相比，他们在多大程度上权衡了外联和推广。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:40
msgid ""
"While the description is comprehensive, here are the key, unwritten tips for"
" winning the top award:"
msgstr "虽然说明很全面，但赢得最高奖项的关键是以下不成文的秘诀："

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:43
msgid ""
"Be a \"Complete Package\": You cannot win Inspire by being excellent in just"
" one area. Your robot must be competitive (a top contender), your portfolio "
"must be comprehensive and professional, and your outreach must be "
"meaningful. Excellence in all judged categories is the goal."
msgstr ""
"成为“全能选手”：仅在某一领域表现卓越无法赢得启发奖。你的机器人必须具备竞争力（一个顶尖竞争者），作品集必须全面且专业，推广活动必须富有意义。在所有评判类别中追求卓越是最终目标。"

#: ../../gm0/source/docs/awards/award-types.rst:49
msgid "Inspire Award Criteria"
msgstr "启发奖标准"

